{"tid":342682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚入]如果你係女人，你會唔會想同一個同自己差唔多嘅男仔拍拖？","createTime":"2017-07-31T20:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T15:05:42.000Z","uid":55552,"like":12,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7bdf6f3ba0abc56bd38bb310fac55543e314b4","tid":342682,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T20:03:18.000Z","msg":"日日係連登見到班毒撚係到叫春，講到自己幾撚高質，明明手都未拖過就講到自己幾咁長情幾咁專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係港女眼中只有洋腸與mk，唔識欣賞自己呢啲絕世好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我不嬲覺得，若果想客觀啲去評價自己，就要學識抽離，問自己若果身邊有個同自己一樣嘅人，你會覺得佢點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以係呢到我想問嘅就係，若然各位覺得自己咁高質，咁我問你，假設你係港女，你會唔會想同一個同現實中嘅自己一模一樣</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\">（性格、樣貌、興趣、賓洲長短etc）</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘅毒撚拍拖，甚至結婚生仔？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔想</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">呢啲嘢無得講大話，小弟先負皮為敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c40824070a185831d4422fb244d71a026b40de7e","tid":342682,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b814e51e2bb5c664e7dba3c413df420f4c7c468","tid":342682,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal